- Solflare (Solana): https://solflare.com/send?address=<address>&amount=<DEFAULT_AMOUNT>
- OKX Wallet (Solana): okxwallet://wallet/send?address=<address>&chain=SOL&amount=<DEFAULT_AMOUNT>
- MetaMask (ETH/MATIC/USDC): https://metamask.app.link/send/<address>?value=<DEFAULT_AMOUNT>
- Coinbase Wallet: https://go.cb-w.com/send?to=<address>&asset=<CHAIN>&amount=<DEFAULT_AMOUNT>
- OKX Wallet (ETH): okxwallet://wallet/send?address=<address>&chain=ETH&amount=<DEFAULT_AMOUNT>
- OKX Wallet (POLYGON): okxwallet://wallet/send?address=<address>&chain=POLYGON&amount=<DEFAULT_AMOUNT>
- BlueWallet (Bitcoin): bitcoin:<address>?amount=<DEFAULT_AMOUNT>
- Trust Wallet (Bitcoin): https://link.trustwallet.com/send?coin=BTC&address=<address>
-->

<section class="donate-container" aria-labelledby="donate-heading">

